name: The Mono Girl
description:
The Mono Girl

she's always cautious. her stare may be blank, but what's inside her mind that counts. You'll never know what specific details she has in her head. 

Flowers, dark flowers growing around her. She's preparing her journey. May her mind and body wander cautiously.

You might meet her in someone's collection. or even your own :)

Love,
Alixos
